{"word":"ἀποκρούω","slug":"ἀποκρούω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>ἀποκρούω</b></el> <p/><div class='li500'><b>I. </b><i>to beat off from</i> a place, <b><a href='S:Xenophon'>Xen.</a></b>:—<a href='S:Medium, Middle'>Mid.</a> <i>to beat off from oneself, beat off</i> an attack, <b><a href='S:Herodotus'>Hdt.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Thucydides'>Thuc.</a></b>: —<a href='S:passive signification'><a href='S:Passive Voice'>Pass.</a></a> <i>to be beaten off</i>, <b><a href='S:Thucydides'>Thuc.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Xenophon'>Xen.</a></b>, <a href='S:et cetera'>etc.</a><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>II. </b><a href='S:passive signification'><a href='S:Passive Voice'>Pass.</a></a>, <el>κοτυλίσκιον τὸ χεῖλος ἀποκεκρουμένον</el> a cup <i>with the</i> lip <i>knocked off</i>, <b><a href='S:Aristophanes'>Ar.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}